T1  - Is there persistence in the growth of manufactured exports? Evidence from newly industrializing countries
AU  - Mody, Ashoka
AU  - Yilmaz, Kamil
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 53
IS  - 2
SP  - 447
EP  - 470
PY  - 1997
DA  - 1997/08/01/
